. LOCALITY RECORDS (
<figureCitation box="[1638,1805,486,523]" captionStart="FIGURE 72" captionStartId="40.[730,821,2705,2734]" captionTargetBox="[516,1890,1648,2689]" captionText="FIGURE 72.—Approximate range of the inflatus and laevis groups." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3828590" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3828590/files/figure.png" pageId="38" pageNumber="35">Figure 72</figureCitation>
